## How to Use This Rule

**This rule activates when a task involves only documentation changes.**

**Agents should:**
1. Recognize documentation trigger keywords
2. Identify all affected documentation files
3. Skip code-related validation steps
4. Focus on documentation standards compliance
5. Verify links and cross-references
6. Update version metadata
7. Commit with `docs(scope): description` format















